{"description":"I would describe this design as a chic bachelor crib of a metro-sexual. Sleek, white furniture, a generous lounge area and glossy surfaces create a stylish interior that looks fashionable and sophisticated, despite its small size.","body":"<p>The arrangement revolves around the conversation area, where the centerpiece is a low, comfortable sectional that can turn into a double bed at night. Light, almost ethereal shelves can hold a substantial collection of books, but are also a great, neutral background for displaying personal objects . The laptop desk doubles as a table, while the bar sits close to it on the balcony.</p>\n<p>The wall between the room and the kitchen received a large window that allows more natural light into the room and an interesting visual contact between the two spaces. Neutral colours complete the refined look, but the blue glass backsplash and the colourful mosaic like rug prevent it from being dull and lifeless.</p>\n<div class=\"pics\">\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 01\" title=\"Picture 01\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-01-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-01-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-01-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-01-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-01.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 02\" title=\"Picture 02\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-02-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-02-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-02-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-02-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-02.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 03\" title=\"Picture 03\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-03-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-03-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-03-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-03-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-03.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 04\" title=\"Picture 04\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-04-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-04-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-04-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-04-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-04.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 05\" title=\"Picture 05\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-05-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-05-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-05-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-05-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-05.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 06\" title=\"Picture 06\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-06-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-06-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-06-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-06-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"urban-sophistication-picture-06.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 07\" title=\"Picture 07\" src=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-07-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/urban-sophistication-picture-07-230x